EU Says Bank Recapitalization Proposal Due in Coming Days

-- B y   P e t e r   C h a p m a n
-- 
2011-10-07T10:33:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/eu-says-bank-recapitalization-proposal-due-in-coming-days.html
The European Commission said it will
make proposals in the coming days on possible coordination of
bank recapitalizations in the European Union.  “There is a window of opportunity indeed, in the coming
days for the commission to present its proposal,” said Olivier
Bailly, a spokesman for the European Commission.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
